gomodel:SYNGO_2534  a     owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Automated change 2024-03-14: GO:0099056 replaced by GO:0042734" , "Rationale: Figure 2: \"Localization of D5 receptor immunoreactivity in GPi and SNr in normal and MPTP-treated monkeys.\"\n- \"(A-D) illustrate D5 receptor immunolabeling in dendrites (Den), unmyelinated axons (Ax) and terminals (Ter) in GPi (A-B) and SNr (C-D) of normal and MPTP-treated monkeys. Occasional glial labeling is also depicted in the SNr (arrowhead in C). Scale bars: 0.5 μm.\"\n\n- Based on the known transmembrane topology of the protein, the \"integral component of ... membrane\" term was chosen.. Experimental description: \"Brain tissue from thirteen (D1, n=11; D5, n=7) Rhesus monkeys (Macacca mulatta, 3-10 kg) w...\"" ;
